= Sergio Magalhães

One of the founders of the *Frente Parlamentar Nacionalista*, a caucus of nationalistic members of Congress. He helped create the *Emenda Constitucional No. 4* that instituted parliamentarism. As a member of the PTB, he supported you during the *Campanha da Legalidade*.

